Add this content to `.gitignore`:
```
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# Virtual Environment
venv/
ENV/
env/

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# Data files (keep code, exclude large data files)
data/processed/*.csv
data/raw/*.csv
logs/
*.log

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Project specific
*.json
~$*
.pytest_cache/
.coverage